      <div about="/ecosleeve.html">
  
    
    <div class="layout layout--onecol">
    <div  class="layout__region layout__region--content">
      <div>
  
    
      
            <div><p>EcoSleeve is typically designed to wrap neatly around a VertiFlow system. It serves as a vital enhancement to the system, providing a variety of benefits that improve both functionality and aesthetics. </p>

<p>Crafted from repurposed clothing such as the leg of a pair of pants or the arm of a shirt, the EcoSleeve is an example of sustainable innovation at its best. This use of pre-existing materials to create a new product reflects a deep commitment to waste reduction, resource efficiency, and environmental preservation. </p>

<p>When added to a VertiFlow system, the EcoSleeve assists with the wicking process, helping to ensure that each VertiCan in the series receives the moisture it needs. Additionally, it provides a sleek, uniform appearance, covering the upcycled cans and creating a cohesive look. </p>

<p>Versatile and eco-conscious, the EcoSleeve can be adapted and used creatively based on the gardener's needs, demonstrating that sustainability and function can indeed go hand in hand.</p>
</div>
      
  </div>
